    "content": "30\nSantoor │ Class 3\nNote to the teacher\nHelp learners recall the consonants and vowels of the English \nalphabet.\nLet us speak\nLet us speak\nDivide into groups of 5. \nEach of you will be one character in the story — circle, \nsquare, triangle, rectangle and the star. \nTake turns and read out the story. \nEnjoy by adding actions to what you say."
