    "content": "32\nSantoor │ Class 3\nB. Write a few lines about your friend by filling in the \nblanks.\nMy Friend\n1. My friend’s name is \n.\n2. He/She is a boy/girl.\n3. He/She is \n years old.\n4. His/Her favourite colour is \n.\n5. He/She likes to play \n.\n6. He/She wants to become \n.\nI love my friend.\nLet us do\nLet us do\nA. Use the space given below to draw the four friends \nyou met in Chapter 3."
