    "page": 51,
    "chapter": "Fun with Words",
    "content": "35\nSantoor │ Class 3\nNote to the teacher\nDraw attention to the action words mentioned in the rhyme.\nWho are you?\nAnd what do you do?\nWe are cats.\nWe mew in the dark.\nWho are you?\nAnd what do you do?\nWe are elephants.\nWe raise our trunks.\nWho are you?\nAnd what do you do?\nWe are lions.\nWe roar and hunt."
