    "content": "42\nSantoor  │ Class 3\nIn the poem, we find —\nrun and skip\njump and sway\nslide and swing\nHere we use ‘and’ to link two words. \nCombine these words using ‘and’ and write them in the \nblanks. One has been done for you.\n1. give, take \n \ngive and take \n2. sing, dance \n3. eat, drink \n4. catch, throw \n5. run, catch \nLet us learn \nLet us learn"
