    "page": 121,
    "chapter": "Chapter10. Night",
    "content": "105\nSantoor │ Class 3\n\u0007And then I go to bed and sleep \nUntil the day begins to peep.  \nAnd when my eyes open,  \nI see the Sun is  \nshining down on me.\nNew words\nwonder \ndistant \npeep"
