    "page": 135,
    "chapter": "Chapter12. Chandrayaan",
    "content": "fused and asked Pratik, “How did \nChandrayaan reach the Moon?”\nPratik \nreplied \nthat \nhis \nfriend \nVivaan’s \nmother, Aunt Nandini, is \na scientist. “Shall we go \nand talk to her?” asked \nPratik. \nRani \nhappily \nagreed. Both Rani and \nPratik decided to visit \nVivaan’s house. \nHave you seen pictures of Chandrayaan landing on \nthe moon?"
