    "content": "128\nSantoor │ Class 3\nNote to the teacher\nThe assessment sheet can be filled by the student under the \nguidance of parents and teachers.\nSELF ASSESSMENT\n1. I can recite the poems \n- in a group. \n \n- in pairs. \n- by repeating after my teacher. \n- by myself. \n2. I can read the stories \n- by myself. \n- with my classmates."
