    "content": "25\nDouble Century\nWrite the numbers in order on the stones.\n \n\u0007Fill a small container like a small bowl with seeds \nsuch as kidney beans, chickpeas, etc. \n \n\u0007Look closely at the container to estimate how many \nseeds are in it. Your Estimate: ......... seeds. \n \n\u0007Now count and see how close your estimation is to \nthe actual number of seeds."
