    "content": "\u0007Now count and see how close your estimation is to \nthe actual number of seeds. Counted ......... seeds.\n \n\u0007Guess how many times you need to fill the \ncontainer to get close to 200 seeds? Your guess: \n......... times. \nI can show \n200 on the \nnumber line too.\n150 + 50 = 200\n140 + 60 = 200\n150\n158\n163\n167\n177\n189\n199\n182"
