    "content": "33\nVacation with My Nani Maa\n–3\n–2\n–10\nThey now have 52 stamps. Nandini and Chirag count \nand find that they have 37 stamps with faces of famous \npersons and the remaining with pictures of \nmonuments.\nHow many stamps with pictures of \nmonuments do they have?\n Stamps – \n Stamps = \n Stamps\n – \n = \n Stamps + \n Stamps = \n Stamps"
