    "content": "35\nVacation with My Nani Maa\nAdding and Subtracting Smartly with the Number Grid\nLet us play a grid \ngame. Each player \ntakes turns rolling \ntwo dice to make a \ntwo-digit number, and \nmoves the counter \nby the number they \nhave made. They \ncan choose to move \nforward or backward. \nThe first to reach a \nnumber between 91"
