    "subject": "Math",
    "page": 54,
    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": "em on the ground.\nWe need to add 25 and 36 to find the total number of radishes.\nred radish \n25\nwhite \nradish 36\nI will add \nusing bundles \nand sticks\n25 red radishes + 36 white radishes = \n radishes\n25 + 36 = \nEstimate the total\nnumber of radishes. \n............\n25 red radishes\nFind other ways of solving the same problem on the number line."
