    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": "a number \nbetween 1 and 10 to the previous \nsum. The player to reach 100 first \nis the winner. An example is given \nhere:\nPlayer 1 wins this round!\nPlay this game with your friends.\nLet us Play\nPlayer 1\nPlayer 2\nTotal\n9\n9\n10\n19\n8\n27\n9\n36\n10\n46\n8\n54\n10\n64\n10\n74\n9\n83\n7\n90\n10\n100"
