    "content": "51\nFun with Shapes\nSame to Same\nMy aunt\ngifted us a board\ngame.\nI wonder what is the \ndifference between a square \nand a rectangle?\nI found a difference. Look at their sides. In a \nrectangle all sides do not necessarily have to \nbe equal in length. It is enough to have just the \nopposite sides be equal in length.\nOh! These"
