    "content": "54\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nSquare corners\nWhich tile will\nfit in the corner of this table?\nWill the same tile fit in the\ncorner of the math\nbook?\nLet us decorate \nthese frames with threads.\nThe corners of a square \nand a rectangle are square \ncorners.\nAre the corners of \nthis shape the same as \nthat of a square \nand a rectangle?"
