    "page": 70,
    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": ".\nAre the corners of \nthis shape the same as \nthat of a square \nand a rectangle?\nAre the corners of a square the same?__________________\nHow do you know?\nPile up some squares over one another and see.\nAre the corners of a rectangle the same?\nHow do you know?\nPile up some rectangles over one another and see.\nAre the corners of the square and a rectangle the same?"
