    "content": "57\nFun with Shapes\nTriangle - Triangle …so many Triangles\nDescribe a Triangle\n1. \n\u0007Draw and name some triangular objects that you see around \nyou, in your notebook.\n3. \n\u0007How many different triangles can be made using \nthe dots on this circle?\n4. \n\u0007Move two matchsticks to turn the one triangle \ninto two triangles.\n2. \nCount the number of triangles in the given rangoli."
