    "id": "m5018",
    "subject": "Math",
    "page": 81,
    "chapter": "House of Hundreds - I",
    "content": ", 110, \n120 … 200, 210, … \n270, 271, 272 … 279, 280\nThese are lots of toffees! \nLet’s count. 10, 20, 30,... \n100, 110, 120, ….190, 200, \n210, …290, 291, 292, \n293, …, 298\n298 and \none more is 299; \n299 and one \nmore is 300."
