    "subject": "Math",
    "page": 86,
    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": "Write it on the number line below. \nCan you show the number using matchsticks?\nOne hundred,\n…two hundred,\n…three hundred,\n...and ???\nFOUR HUNDRED\n0\n100\n200\n300\n?"
