    "content": "83\nRaksha Bandhan\nLet’s make Rakhis\nLook! My teacher\nhas taught us to make \nRakhis.\nWe need to make\n5 Rakhis. \nFor each Rakhi we need one flower, \n.......... threads and .......... beads.\nHow many threads, flowers and beads do \nthey need?\nCelebration begins!\nDhara’s mother has bought some material for the festival.\nGuess the festival they are preparing for.\nRaksha bandhan!"
