    "content": "94\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nVisit to a Farm\nThe next day the children take their Appa and cousins to the farm. \nThey see a lot of chickens there. Let us count chickens in the farm!\n1 times 2 \nis 2 \nor 1 × 2 \n= 2\n2 times 2 \nis 4 \nor 2 × 2 \n= 4\n3 times 2 \nis 6 \nor 3 × 2 \n= 6\n4 times 2 \nis ....... \nor 4 × 2 \n= .......\n5 times 2"
