    "chapter": "Raksha Bandhan",
    "content": "6 × 1 = 6\n 7 × 1 = 7\n 8 × 1 = 8\n 9 × 1 = 9\n 10 × 1 = 10\n 1 × 6 = 6\n 2 × 6 = 12\n 3 × 6 = 18\n 4 × 6 = 24\n 5 × 6 = 30\n 6 × 6 = 36\n 7 × 6 = 42\n 8 × 6 = 48\n 9 × 6 = 54\n 10 × 6 = 60\n 1 × 2 = 2\n 2 × 2 = 4\n 3 × 2 = 6\n 4 × 2 = 8\n 5 × 2 = 10\n 6 × 2 = 12\n 7 × 2 = 14\n 8 × 2 = 16\n 9 × 2 = 18\n 10 × 2 = 20\n 1 × 7 = 7\n 2 × 7 = 14\n 3 × 7 = 21"
