    "page": 141,
    "chapter": "2. Make other numbers.",
    "content": "00 written on them. \nSix hundred.\nFour slips with 100 \nwritten on them and two \nslips with 10 on them. \n420\n100\n100\n100\n100\n100\n100\n100\n100\n100\n10\n100\n10\n2. Make other numbers.\nNumber is .........\nNumber is .........\n1. \u0007I have 6 blank paper slips. I can write 100, 10 or 1 on each of \nthem. What numbers can I make with these 6 slips?"
