    "chapter": "Fun at Class Party!",
    "content": "135\nFun at Class Party!\nMeasure your height by marking one metre on the wall of your class. \nWrite the names of your friends whose heights are more than one \nmetre and whose heights are less than one metre.\nWho is the tallest among them? Discuss.\nCircle the tallest among these children:\nHeights more than one metre\n_________________ _________________"
