    "chapter": "2. Find the vessels at home that are exactly 1 litre.",
    "content": "courage \nchildren to establish in class that 4 quarter litre glasses are equal \nto 1 litre, and 2 half litre mugs are equal to 1 litre.\nFirst guess and check with the 1 litre bottle.\na) \n\u0007How much water does a bucket hold at your home: \nmore than/less than/equal to 1 litre.\nb) \n\u0007How much water does a mug hold at your home:"
