    "content": "148\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nTeacher’s Note: Have discussions with children in the class as to how \nchildren are making their guesses. Encourage children to discover/\ndiscuss relationships between 1 kg, ½ kg, and ¼ kg using the pan-\nbalance and the 1 kg salt packet. \nLook around your house and identify objects that are about half"
