    "content": "salt packet. \nLook around your house and identify objects that are about half \na kilogram and quarter of a kilogram. Feel these things with \nyour hand and guess what other things are a half or quarter \nkilogram. List the objects that are about a quarter kilogram and \na half kilogram. Verify with the 1 kilogram salt packet."
