    "content": "154\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nWrite word problems using the numbers given in the box \ndiagrams below and solve them. You can take help from the \npictures for appropriate contexts.\nDraw box diagrams, as shown above to solve the following \nproblems. Then use HTO blocks or a number line to solve the \nproblems.\n1. \u0007Kishan has 456 saplings in August."
