    "content": "or a number line to solve the \nproblems.\n1. \u0007Kishan has 456 saplings in August. He distributed 63 \nsaplings. How many saplings are left with him?\n2. \u0007Kishan has a collection of 309 saplings. He gets 80 more \nsaplings of flowering plants. How many saplings does he \nhave now?\n3. \u0007Kishan has 270 saplings of herbs and his friend has 36"
