    "subject": "Math",
    "page": 172,
    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": "ople in this \nvillage had to give different quantities \nwhile exchanging things.\nThese days we use money in exchange for things we need. \nNotes and coins come in different values which are used to \nbuy different things. \nAdd 100\nAdd 100\nAdd 10\nAdd 10\nAdd 1\nAdd 1\n269\n454\n269\n454\n269\n454\n369\n455\n289"
