    "id": "m7793",
    "subject": "Math",
    "page": 176,
    "chapter": "Maths Mela | Class 3",
    "content": "160\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nIn the morning, Peter uncle has ` 465 in his money box. By \nafternoon, he has ` 756. How much has he earned since \nmorning?\nMy Estimation.\n` ____________\nLet us draw a box diagram for the \nproblem.\n465\n` 756\nDifference between the two amounts = ` 291\nHe has earned ` 291 since morning.\n756\n?\nTake out ` 465"
