    "page": 187,
    "chapter": "Time Goes On",
    "content": "morning.\n(a) 07:00\n(a) 8:15 or quarter past 8\n(b) 8:30 or half past 8\n(b) 07:15\nShe took ______________ minutes to eat her breakfast. How \ndo you know?\n2. \n\u0007Draw the hour hand and minute hand on the clock to \nshow the following:\nLet us Play\nTeacher’s Note: Discuss with children what the numbers and marks on the clock mean."
