    "content": "188\nMaths Mela | Class 3\nkulfi\nGiant Wheel \nRead the conversation between Soni and\nAvi and mark the place they are talking about.\nImagine yourself sitting with Soni and Avi. You think of \na place or a stall and challenge your friend to find out \nwhich stall you have in your mind. You can help them \nguess by answering yes or no."
