    "content": "ok around, as far as you can see. Remember \nto look down near your feet as well! \n• How many kinds of trees, shrubs, herbs, grasses, \nclimbers or creepers can you spot?\n1\n \nMarigold \nNeem \nJujube or ber\n (Banthi in Telugu) \n(Bevugida in Kannada) (Boroi in Manipuri)\n \n__________________ \n__________________ \n__________________"
