    "id": "s11983",
    "subject": "Science",
    "page": 130,
    "chapter": "Our Wondrous World | Class 3",
    "content": "ximum number \nof times. \nThen, invite a friend to start jumping after you skip \n10 times or after you say a short poem as you skip. For \nexample:\nI like roti,\nI like ghee.\nI want _______________________,\n(name of a friend)\nTo jump with me!\n\u0007What other games do you play with a skipping rope? \nTeach and learn from your friends."
