    "content": "Staying Healthy and Happy\n117\nPlaying safely\nIt is important to be safe while having fun. Which \nof the following places is considered a safe area to \nplay? Why or why not?\nA construction site\nSafe\nUnsafe\nA roof without railings\nSafe\nUnsafe\nA park\nSafe\nUnsafe\nA busy road\nSafe\nUnsafe\nA schoolground\nSafe\nUnsafe\n2025-26"
